OL,7,FBritain's regulators have little idea
OL,8,Fhow much sewage is poured into rivers
OL,9,Fby water companies because of a lack of
OL,10,Fsensors, i has learned.
OL,12,FDocuments published online and seen by
OL,13,Fi reveal a failure to install sensors
OL,14,Fto monitor sewage flow levels at many
OL,15,Fsewage treatment plants.
OL,17,FEven where meters were in place to
OL,18,Frecord how much waste was being treated
OL,19,Fand discharged, there were failures to
OL,20,Fcheck they were working properly or to
OL,21,Fmake best use of them.
OL,3,CRegulators don't know how much sewage
OL,4,Cis being pumped into rivers, because of
OL,5,Ca lack of sensors
